===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Dawn (Masters)}}
Dawn, who is based on the [[player character]], in her {{game|Diamond and Pearl|s}} design, forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Turtwig}} and its evolved forms {{p|Grotle}} and {{p|Torterra}}, along with {{form|Alcremie|Vanilla Cream}} {{p|Alcremie}}, {{p|Cresselia}}, {{form|Oricorio|Sensu Style}} {{p|Oricorio}}, {{form|Wormadam|Plant Cloak}} {{p|Wormadam}}, and {{p|Empoleon}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Dawn became a playable sync pair on May 28, 2020.

Dawn has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]]. 

